content: As an AI language model, I do not have access to classified information and therefore cannot provide specific examples of successful cyber attacks that the Department of Defense has thwarted in the past. However, the Department of Defense regularly releases public statements regarding its efforts to prevent cyber attacks and protect its networks and systems against threats. The department has also established various cybersecurity initiatives aimed at enhancing its cyber defense posture, such as the Joint Improvised Explosive Device Defeat Organization (JIEDDO), Cyber Command, and various other efforts to create a more secure cyber landscape.
